      "date": "2025-03-30 04:29:47.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified-1\n\nBuild Failed \n\nhttps://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/112092/ : FAILURE",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
